response.original_title: Bombers Post WWII: Avro Vulcan and Panavia Tornado
response.overview: The Avro Vulcan and the Panavia Tornado were completed their development after the conclusion of World War II. This documentary uses footage and commentary captured shortly after the release of these new bombers which explain the impressive and "new" features of these planes, and provide insight about where the technology was at that time.
response.title: Bombers Post WWII: Avro Vulcan and Panavia Tornado
